quran[25]{c,v,t}:
  29,1,"Alif, Laam, Miim"
  29,2,"E yimЙ“e Й“en sikku Й“e accirte nii, fii Й“e wi'ii: \"Men gomЙ—inii!\" Hara Й“e fitninaaka"
  29,3,"GomЙ—ii, Men fitninii Й“en adinooЙ“e Й“e. Maa Alla feГұГұin, fii goonguЙ“e Й“en, maa O feГұГұin kadi, fii fenooЙ“e Й“en"
  29,4,"Kaa huuwuЙ“e bonЙ—i Й“en sikku, wonnde Й“e laawoto Men? ko Й“e Гұaawata kon bonii"
  29,5,"Kala tawЙ—o himo jortii hawroygol e Alla, ko pellet, lajal Alla ngal, ko hewtaygal. Ko Kanko woni Nanoowo, AnnduЙ—o On"
  29,6,"Kala kadi tiiЙ—niiЙ—o, ko hoore-makko o tiiЙ—nanii, tawde pellet, Alla ko yonndiniiЙ—o e tageefo ngon"
  29,7,"ЖҒen non gomЙ—imЙ“e, Й“e golli golle moЖҙЖҙe, ma Men momtan Й“e bonЙ—i maЙ“Й“e Й—in, Men yoЙ“itra Й“e, ko Й“uri moЖҙЖҙude e ko Й“e gollaynoo kon"
  29,8,"Men yamirii neЙ—Й—anke on, moЖҙЖҙugol e mawЙ“e makko Й“en. Si Й“e doolii maa fii sirkangol Lam, ko a alanaa Й—um ganndal, wata a Й—ofto Й“e ! Ko ka Am, woni ruttorde mon, Mi habra on, ko gollaynoЙ—on"
  29,9,"ЖҒen gomЙ—imЙ“e Alla, Й“e golli golle moЖҙЖҙe, ma Men waЙ—tiduЙ“e e moЖҙЖҙuЙ“e Й“en"
  29,10,"Hino e jimЙ“e Й“en, wi'oowo: \"Men gomЙ—inii Alla\"; hara non si o tampiniraama fii Alla, o waЙ—ay lorra yimЙ“e Й“en, wano lepte Alla Й—en. Si ballal kadi immorii ka Joomi maa, pellet, Й“e wi'ay: \"MeЙ—en wondunoo e mo'on!\" Kere wanaa Alla Й“uri anndude ko woni e Й“erЙ—e tageefo ngon"
  29,11,"Ma Alla anndin fii gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“en, ma O feГұГұina kadi fii naafiqiiЙ“e Й“en"
  29,12,"HeeferЙ“e Й“en wi'ani gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“en: \"Jokkee laawol amen ngol, men fawtoto fii goopi mon Й—in\". Kono Й“e wonaali fawtotooЙ“e hay huunde e goopi maЙ“Й“e. Pellet, ko Й“e fenooЙ“e"
  29,13,"Kono maa Й“e fawtoo fii teddeendi junuubi maЙ“Й“e Й—in, e teddeendi goo, wonndude e teddeendi maЙ“Й“e ndin. Ko maa Й“e lamndoyee, Г‘alnde Darngal, gaay e kon ko Й“e fefindotonoo"
  29,14,"GomЙ—ii Men nulii Nuuhu e yimЙ“e makko Й“en, o ГұiiЙ“i hakkunde maЙ“Й“e, duuЙ“i ujunere, ЕӢakkuЙ—um duuЙ“i cappanЙ—e jowi. Waame on nanngi Й“e, hari ko Й“e tooГұuЙ“e"
  29,15,"Men daЙ—ndi mo, kanko e yimЙ“e laana kan; Men waЙ—i ka kaawisa tageefo ngon"
  29,16,"(Janto) kadi Ibraahiima, nde o wi'annoo yimЙ“e makko Й“en: \"Rewee Alla, hulon Mo; ko Й—um Й“uri moЖҙЖҙannde on, si woni hiЙ—on anndi"
  29,17,"Anndee ko reweton kon gaanin Alla, ko sanamuuji, hiЙ—on taЖҙa fenaande. Pellet, Й—in Й—i rewoton gaanin Alla, Й—i waawaa on arsikude; Й—aЙ“Й“iree arsike on ka Alla, rewon Mo, yetton Mo. Ko ka Makko woni rutteteЙ—on"
  29,18,"Si on fennii, haray mofte adinooЙ“e kadi fenniino (NulaaЙ“e mun). Alaa ko fawii e NulaaЙ—o on, si wanaa yottingol Й“annginngol"
  29,19,"E Й“ee yi'aali no Alla fuЙ—Й—orta tagu ngun, refti O ruttay ngu? Pellet, Й—um wonii ko newanii Alla"
  29,20,"Maaku: \"Yiilee ka leydi, ndaaron no O fuЙ—Й—ori tagu ngun. Refti Alla taga tagu sakkitoru ngun. Pellet, Alla ko hattanЙ—o kala huunde"
  29,21,"Himo lepte mo O muuyani, O yurmo mo O muuyani; ko ka Makko rutteteЙ—on"
  29,22,"On wonaali laawotooЙ“e ka leydi, wanaa ka kammu; alanaa on gaanin Alla, woni giЙ—o, wanaa ballo"
  29,23,"ЖҒen yedduЙ“e Aayeeje Alla Й—en, e hawroygol e Makko ngol, Й“en taЖҙike e yurmeende Am, Й“en Й—on, hino woodani Й“e lepte muusuЙ—e"
  29,24,"Jaabawol yimЙ“e makko Й“en wonaano, si wanaa wiide Й“e: \"Waree mo, maa sunnon mo\". Kono Alla daЙ—ndi mo e yiite ngen. Pellet, wonii e Й—um, maandeeji, wonannde yimЙ“e gomЙ—imЙ“e"
  29,25,"O maaki: \"Anndee ko rewoton kon gaanin Alla, ko sanamuuji, fii yiЙ—indiro hakkunde mon, ka nguurndam aduna, hooti non, Г‘alnde Darndal, yoga mon yeddoyay yoga, yoga mon kadi huЙ—o yoga, hara non, jaaЖҙorde mon nden, ko ka Yiite, hara wallooЙ“e alanaa on"